!     TURBO-C / VGA
!
!     DEFINE THE 4 GENERAL TURBO-C SWITCHES.
!     NOTE--THERE ARE 4 TURBO-C SWITCHES--
!           1. TCLOAD
!              HAS CMAIN.EXE BEEN LOADED (& INIT. EXEC.)? YES/NO
!           2. TCMENU
!              IS THE TURBO C MENU ON/OFF THE SCREEN?     ON/OFF
!           3. TCPLFI
!              WHAT IS STATUS OF THE TURBO C PLOT FILE?   OPEN/CLOS
!           4. TCTEFI
!              WHAT IS STATUS OF THE TURBO C TEXT FILE?   OPEN/CLOS
!     NOTE--THEY ARE INITIALLY ALLOCATED IN DPCODV.INC
!           THEY ARE INITIALLY DEFINED   IN INITOD.FOR
!           THEY ARE USED                IN TCDRIV.FOR & CMAIN.C
!
